course_title: World Music Ensembles - BALINSE GAMLN EN

sections.comments: BALINESE GAMELAN ENSEMBLE. For graduate students (undergraduates register in MUSC 165B 001).OPEN TO NON-MUSIC STUDENTS: The gamelan is open to all without audition.For the 2020W academic year, please contact instructor (michael.tenzer@ubc.ca) for permission to register.http://www.music.ubc.ca/index.php?id=2011

description: Training on traditional instruments and their techniques, with emphasis on ensemble performance. Different sections focus on the music of different cultures, e.g., Bali, China, Ghana, Korea.
